@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fbkrxq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    v2 = 0.06
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.75 * v0 + 0.73) / (v1 + 0.71 * v2 + 0.73)) + wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.55)))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
